	line `In advancing and in retreating, The perseverance of a warrior furthers.`
	line `Penetration under the bed. Priests and magicians are used in great number. Good fortune. No blame.`
	line `Repeated penetration. Humiliation.`
	line `Remorse vanishes. During the hunt Three kinds of game are caught.`
	line `Perseverance brings good fortune. Remorse vanishes. Nothing that does not further. No beginning, but an end. Before the change, three days. After the change, three days. Good fortune.`
	line `Penetration under the bed. He loses his property and his ax. Perseverance brings misfortune.`
