	line `Being prepared brings good fortune. If there are secret designs, it is disquieting.`
	line `A crane calling in the shade. Its young answers it. I have a good goblet. I will share it with you.`
	line `He finds a comrade. Now he beats the drum, now he stops. Now he sobs, now he sings.`
