	line `The bird meets with misfortune through flying.`
	line `She passes by her ancestor And meets her ancestress. He does not reach his prince And meets the official. No blame.`
	line `If one is not extremely careful, Somebody may come up from behind and strike him. Misfortune.`
	line `No blame. He meets him without passing by. Going brings danger. One must be on guard. Do not act. Be constantly persevering.`
	line `Dense clouds, No rain from our western territory. The prince shoots and hits him who is in the cave.`
	line `He passes him by, not meeting him. The flying bird leaves him. Misfortune. This means bad luck and injury.`
